ke":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b4c33c5619bfa8fb071a2179b3ab0c06653b194f","tid":1945352,"uid":214192,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"quote":{"pid":"7da7ca1a9a089c9a86a7d20b5700f8919e8a4a0e","tid":1945352,"uid":2110,"like":243,"dislike":3,"score":240,"quote":{"pid":"6e95d3fd806fb3753025b90ad147c3fca7bac1c8","tid":1945352,"uid":152476,"like":265,"dislike":1,"score":264,"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T03:53:36.000Z","msg":"又話沒事兒？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T03:55:51.000Z","msg":"我懷疑係有心令當地物資短缺"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T05:55:25.000Z","msg":"我覺得係搶曬人地啲物資 跟住話捐返出去<br />\n造就支那神話<br />\n真係得佢哋先可以咁無恥"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T06:16:06.000Z","msg":"賣呀，唔會捐"},{"pid":"449487a2cb60a96008fc5deafbf0f54dd5b8bd25","tid":1945352,"uid":199957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d052ac0593fe9be3def7dd313561b81fc24d2d8","tid":1945352,"uid":56015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T03:52:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.post852.com/300838/【武漢肺炎】國企命員工全球採購抗疫物資返國%e3%80%80/?fbclid=IwAR3BXEAqnLKSzAciXoI8dlbapZl7FLme6Xa69xgixd4-giTTDa7gof8Nt04\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F300838%2F%E3%80%90%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%91%E5%9C%8B%E4%BC%81%E5%91%BD%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E6%8E%A1%E8%B3%BC%E6%8A%97%E7%96%AB%E7%89%A9%E8%B3%87%E8%BF%94%E5%9C%8B%25e3%2580%2580%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3BXEAqnLKSzAciXoI8dlbapZl7FLme6Xa69xgixd4-giTTDa7gof8Nt04&d=UCgs38VSsqZrRa6JqpzgNoGitI067obQ02bu1xQE4oc%3D&h=db882cef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.post852.com/300838/【武漢肺炎】國企命員工全球採購抗疫物資返國%e3%80%80/?fbclid=IwAR3BXEAqnLKSzAciXoI8dlbapZl7FLme6Xa69xgixd4-giTTDa7gof8Nt04</a><br />\n<br />\n【武漢肺炎】中國國企命員工全球採購抗疫物資返國 涉300萬口罩50萬醫用手套<br />\n<br />\n2020-3-26 21:00<br />\n字體： A A A <br />\n武漢新型冠狀病毒肺炎疫情蔓延全球，各地都有人搶購防疫物資。澳洲報章《雪梨晨鋒報（The Sydney Morning Herald）》引述消息稱，經營國際房地產業務的中國國企綠地控股集團（Greenland Group），早前要求澳洲、加拿大、土耳其及其他地區的員工暫停正常工作，改為在當地採購大量抗疫物資運返中國，涉及300萬個口罩、50萬對醫用手套、70萬套全身保護衣物、探熱針、大量酒精搓手液及消毒濕紙巾等。<br />\n知情人士向該報表示，這項工作持續了數周，橫跨今年1至2月。基本上所有員工都需要搜羅醫療用品，而員工本身大多數是中國人。<br />\n集團向該報發聲明，證實曾於1至2月將抗疫物資運返中國，綠地澳洲公司亦支持該集團的提議。由於疫情導致中國抗疫物資短缺，集團致力協助減輕病毒傳播。<br />\n報道亦引述其他媒體報道指，綠地澳洲公司總經理羅曉華（Sherwood Luo）曾於2月在微信上發文，指集團正將第二批非接觸式額頭探熱器運往中國。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T06:17:13.000Z","msg":"又話冇事 屌你老母 而家又有事"},{"pid":"4bb22f438a66ef067f7812abc3e047014378a0a5","tid":1945352,"uid":77731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T06:19:28.000Z","msg":"仲採？咪初步抗疫成功"},{"pid":"43318361047939f221502199d4b7ae3f388401b4","tid":1945352,"uid":201374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6e95d3fd806fb3753025b90ad147c3fca7bac1c8","tid":1945352,"uid":152476,"like":265,"dislike":1,"score":264,"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T03:53:36.000Z","msg":"又話沒事兒？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T06:20:49.000Z","msg":"今年1至2月"},{"pid":"1b69da5baf3ec181a68c57a84ccf7bde0c7edf7d","tid":1945352,"uid":201374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T06:21:53.000Z","msg":"標題嚴重誤導，拉"},{"pid":"fdfba80626618c38f4310417b7099ee592aeefdf","tid":1945352,"uid":65074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T06:23:24.000Z","msg":"等睇全世界驅逐中國人"},{"pid":"31a309616b1a159db9cc1c41e9af53768ae1b220","tid":1945352,"uid":25468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T06:27:04.000Z","msg":"內文講 1-2 月 , 有邊個唔知 ?<br />\n<br />\n而家 4 月都黎緊 , 標題話「又再開始全球搶物資」, 以為而家仲搶緊<br />\n<br />\n不過好多人無睇內容就覆 , 又會變左 fake news"},{"pid":"cc8d8ba869c07ad386d06cb406f70af63256f857","tid":1945352,"uid":106800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T06:30:24.000Z","msg":"推上TWITTER啦 國際線!!!"},{"pid":"b51b7189cbe5b6ca1100b22b81b4a9f2ebd6ae61","tid":1945352,"uid":74935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T06:32:50.000Z","ms